"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Open Source Repositories\\n\\nPlease find the open source repositories on our [GitHub](https://github.com/dydxprotocol):\\n\\n* [Monorepo](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain)\\n    * [Protocol](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/tree/main/protocol)\\n    * [Indexer](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/tree/main/indexer)\\n* [Clients](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients)\\n* [Frontend](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-web)\\n* [iOS](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-native-ios)\\n* [Android](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-native-android)\\n* [Terraform](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-infrastructure)\\n\\nWhen contributing, please ensure your commits are verified. You can follow these steps to do so:\\n* [Generate a new signing key](https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/generating-a-new-gpg-key) for work use and [turn on Vigilant Mode](https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/displaying-verification-statuses-for-all-of-your-commits)\\n* [Tell Git about your GPG key](https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/telling-git-about-your-signing-key) and install `pinentry` if necessary\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/repositories#open-source-repositories\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>Please find the open source repositories on our <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol\\\">GitHub</a>:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain\\\">Monorepo</a>\\n<ul>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/tree/main/protocol\\\">Protocol</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/tree/main/indexer\\\">Indexer</a></li>\\n</ul>\\n</li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients\\\">Clients</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-web\\\">Frontend</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-native-ios\\\">iOS</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-native-android\\\">Android</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-infrastructure\\\">Terraform</a></li>\\n</ul>\\n<p>When contributing, please ensure your commits are verified. You can follow these steps to do so:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/generating-a-new-gpg-key\\\">Generate a new signing key</a> for work use and <a href=\\\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/displaying-verification-statuses-for-all-of-your-commits\\\">turn on Vigilant Mode</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/telling-git-about-your-signing-key\\\">Tell Git about your GPG key</a> and install <code>pinentry</code> if necessary</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/repositories.mdx#open-source-repositories\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nPlease find the open source repositories on our GitHub:\\n\\nMonorepo\\n\\nProtocol\\nIndexer\\n\\n\\nClients\\nFrontend\\niOS\\nAndroid\\nTerraform\\n\\nWhen contributing, please ensure your commits are verified. You can follow these steps to do so:\\n\\nGenerate a new signing key for work use and turn on Vigilant Mode\\nTell Git about your GPG key and install pinentry if necessary\\n\",\"title\":\"Open Source Repositories\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
